job.plaincontent:
- Technical face to the customer for all pre-sales activities for RF products;
- Responsible for understanding the technical requirements of customers as they relate to impedance matching networks 
and RF power generators;
- Take technical ownership of customers;
- Work closely with other departments to develop initial prototypes and refine them to gain customer acceptance;
- Get information on new opportunities from technical departments at customers;
- Participate in the finalization of documentation required to ensure proper production of volume products based on 
optimizations done in the prototyping process;
- Communicate closely with other departments, both in China and in other locations, including sales, quality and 
production
